Peking Opera makeup is derived from the 200-year-old opera art, combining Chinese history and traditional aesthetics. The symbolism of the colors and the exquisiteness of the details have impressed many. To those whom Peking Opera deeply intrigues, especially young people in China today, being able to experience Peking Opera makeup and even a full dress-up at an affordable price can certainly be good news. By stepping into a Peking Opera character, one can not only experience the external makeover but the internal cultural trip as well.